		"description": "<p><strong>Crafting Components:</strong> Fire from the Plane of Fire, powdered fiend horn</p><hr class=\"a5e-rule u-my-md\"><p>This gorgeous necklace is affixed with [[/r 1d6+3 #beads]] beads that radiate power. You can use an action to hurl a bead up to 60 feet. When the bead lands it detonates as a 3rd-level @Compendium[a5e.a5e-spells.47oifxu4ytkf7alt]{Fireball} (save DC 15).</p><p>You can hurl multiple beads with the same action, increasing the spell level of the fireball by 1 for each bead beyond the first. <br></p>",
